graph.description: This resource model describes heritage resources, which includes monuments, buildings, structures, etc.
graph.name: Heritage Resource Model

cards.description:
Describes the physical location of a resource.

Relates to Activity E7 with P7
Relates to Heritage Resource E18 with P53
Relates to Heritage Resource Group E27 with P89
Relates to Actor E39 with P74 (this restricts the place to former and current residences, which can be as broad or narrow)
Relates to Historical Event E5 with P7
Relates to Information Resource E73 with P67
cards.name: Place

cards.description: Represents a single node in a graph
cards.instructions: Describe the assessed condition of the resource.
cards.name: Condition Description

cards.description:
This branch evaluates instances of Heritage Resource E18 and Heritage Resource Group E27

Relates to E18 and E27 resource models via P140i.
cards.name: Evaluation

cards.description:
Describes the type and time span of the beginning of a resource's existence.

Relates to the Actor resource model E39 via P92i.
Relates to Historic Event E5 and Activity E7 via p116i.
cards.instructions: Please enter the date of the beginning of existence for the resource.
cards.name: Beginning of Existence

cards.description: Describes the conditions, threats, and disturbances affecting a Heritage Resource or Heritage Resource Group. Additional information may include a management recommendation, a condition image, the data the condition was assessed and a description of the condition.
cards.name: Condition Assessment

cards.instructions: Describe a related/ancillary feature  and the cultural period and/or date range for the feature.
